{"word":"ὑποτελής","slug":"ὑποτελής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑποτελής</b></el> <el>(ὑπο-τελής, ές) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:τέλος'><el>τέλος</el></a> IV\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>subject to pay taxes, taxable, tributary</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>vectigalis</el>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; in full, <el>ὑποτελὴς φόρου</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <i>receiving as payment</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}